  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00181', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-114-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '聯合國教科文組織界定，當一個國家老年人口的比例至少超過全國多少的比例，可稱之為老年國？', '["6%", "7%", "8%", "9%"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2b3770e8743a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e496b24c7c76", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "505", "s": "0404", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00182', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-114-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作者為吸引更多人關心受災戶，未經受災戶同意，擅自將受災戶個人隱私洩漏給媒體，讓其大肆報 導，此係違反下列何種倫理守則？', '["尊重意見，不越俎代庖", "專心服務，實事求是", "尊重他人，維護隱私", "珍惜資源，拒謀私利，不牽涉政治、宗教、商業行為"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2b3770e8743a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e496b24c7c76", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "505", "s": "0404", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
